Normal PetRare Pet

Dolphin
(Adult)
Animated:

An intelligent dolphin, able to move fast through the water. It will always thank you for all the fish.

Dolphin is a pet. It hatches from a Dolphin egg.

Requirement To Gain Experience

  • While in Underwater location.

Names

These are the default names this pet can have when it first hatches:

  • Alpha
  • Beta
  • Bubbles
  • Ecco
  • Flipper
  • JoJo
  • Snorky
  • Snowflake
  • Tricky
  • Winter

Trick Dolphin
(Adult)
Animated:

This dolphin is always picking up things to bounce and do tricks with! Look at it go!

Trick Dolphin is a rare pet. It hatches from a rare Dolphin egg.

Requirement To Gain Experience

  • While in Underwater location.

Names

These are the default names this pet can have when it first hatches:

  • Alpha
  • Beta
  • Bubbles
  • Ecco
  • Flipper
  • JoJo
  • Snorky
  • Snowflake
  • Tricky
  • Winter

Egg

Dolphin
(Egg)
Animated:

This pet is an Egg from level 0 to level 1.

Experience To Hatch

  • Requires an additional 35,000 experience to advance to level 1. (35,000 total experience required)
    • This pet will become a Juvenile when it reaches level 1.

This pet is a Juvenile from level 1 to 4.

Experience To Grow

  • Requires an additional 50,000 experience to advance to level 2. (85,000 total experience required)
  • Requires an additional 65,000 experience to advance to level 3. (150,000 total experience required)
  • Requires an additional 100,000 experience to advance to level 4. (250,000 total experience required)
    • This pet will become an Adult when it reaches level 4.

Ability

   Torpedo Away
Effect Requirements Cooldowns Charges
Completes 10 Underwater Traveling actions instantly. While traveling.
While in Underwater location.		 5,000 steps
While in Underwater location.		 5
Your Dolphin propels itself in front of you while heading toward your next watery destination. The slipstream current pulls you in and allows you effortlessly arrive there in no time at all.
